  "formula": "1d100",
  "description": "<p>The nucleus of the living world is one of the focal points of this vast organism. If you are on an expedition without a specific mission, these areas can serve as your destination. Use the table below to reveal what vital organ lies there.</p><p>If you interact with a nucleus, envision how the world is affected by it. If a vital organ ends up damaged, how does the whole organism suffer? If this affectation constitutes the death of the planet, how does it manifest? What is a necrotic living world like and how do other organisms survive this environmental change?</p>",
